<br>
Bladestopper -  WAR, CLR, PAL, RNG, SHD, BRD, ROG, SHM<br>
Orb of Tishan - BRD, NEC, WIZ, MAG, ENC<br>
Blight, Hammer of the Scourge - SHM<br>
Prayers of Life - ALL<br>
Cloak of Flames - Melee Classes Only (Even though this is an all/all item)<br>
Red Dragon Tooth - ALL<br>
Gauntlets of Fiery Might - WAR, PAL, RNG, SHD, MNK, BRD, ROG<br>
Selo's Drums of the March - BRD<br>
Gold Plated Koshigatana - WAR, RNG, SHD, BRD, ROG, NEC, WIZ, MAG, ENC<br>
Treasure Hunter's Satchel - ALL<br>
Heirophant's Crook - DRU<br>
<br>
The only item that is restricted from its normal users on this list is the Cloak of Flames. Like Torbin's Eyepatch, I'm of the opinion that only a certain set of classes will benefit from this item (i.e. melee classes). I'm posting this so there will be no surprises. <br>
<br>
[Edit 2/5/01]<br>
<br>
The Red Scale does indeed drop off of Nagafen, and is used in the Red Dragonscale armour. It is not no drop, so we'll lotto it if it drops. The BP is usable by War, Pal, Rng, Shd, Brd and Rog so those are the classes able to lotto for it. <br>
<br>
This piece is indeed for the Warrior AND Bard epic quest weapon as well. However, I'm not going to restrict the lotto on it, as all the classes that can use the BP could benefit from the BP. <br>
<br>
[Edit 2/5/01}<br>
I'm also going to list the fire giant loot, because we will probably get this too. <br>
<br>
King Trannix<br>
Crown of King Tranix - All/All <br>
Polished Mitrhil Torque - PAL, RNG, SHD, BRD (restricting this one to just the classes who use the stats) NO DROP (will lotto before approaching the throne room)<br>
<br>
Magus Roykl<br>
Polished Mithril Mask - (RNG, SHD, PAL, DRU, SHM, ENC, CLR, WIZ, MAG, NEC, MNK) NO DROP<br>
Roykl's Channeling Crystal - BRD, NEC, WIZ, MAG, ENC<br>
<br>
Warlord Skarlon <br>
Mithril Greaves - WAR, PAL, RNG, SHD, BRD, ROG<br>
Mithril Vambraces - WAR, PAL, RNG, SHD, BRD, ROG<br>
Razing Sword of Skarlon - WAR, PAL, SHD<br>
<br>
The only restricted FG gear is the Mitrhil torque and the mithril mask. <br>
<br>
[Edit 2/9/01]<br>
<br>
Nagafen's Book of Scale is used in the Paladin epic quest. All paladins will pre-roll for this book before we fight Nagafen in case it drops. <br>
<br>
BUMP - 3/21/01<br>
<br>
This goes for all Sacred Band-led Nagafen raids until further notice.<br>
<br>
